name: DYOR Analyzer
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
No more flipping between endless tabs, wasting precious time, and missing out on those golden entry points. With $DYOR all your shitcoin needs will be right at your fingertips. This is a memecoin with the goal of creating a coin analyzer with deep analytical and reporting power. 

What makes your project unique?
We released a functioning alpha version of our product before launching. Had many communities back us and become very bullish, supporting us. Our analyzer is available publicly right now at dyoranalyzer.com

Our original goal stands, and is still in development.

History of your project.
We have just launched our project today, after raising 114.6 ETH.

What’s next for your project?
Finishing our project as promised, we are looking to add more functionalities to our current analyzer and become the #1 coin analyzer in the entire market. 

What can your token be used for?
Our token is a memecoin.
